setear en metatrader4 los indicadores del primer curso para ver los highs and lows de dia, semana y mes.

EMA indicator setearlo 10 dias rojo y 20 dias azul para ver el movimiento del precio y ver donde se cruzan para que de senal de compra o venta.
Use the indicator MACD below the chart to read where a signal for buying or selling its about to happen
using RSI (relative strenght Index) indicator to be atble to see buy and sell signals, Over 70 sell, Under 30 Buy, Alternatively over 80 sell, Alternatively under 20 Buy.

Head and shoulders pattern either way goes to consolidation and then to bullish or bearish.

